Method.ЗначенияРеквизитовОбъекта.Param.Реквизиты.Type.1.Description=where the key passed is\nthe alias of a field for the returned structure with the result, and the value (optionally)\nis the actual field name in the table.\nIf the key is set and the value is undefined, the field name is taken from the key.
