Method.ПроверитьИмяПроцедурыКонфигурации.Description=Checks that the passed name ProcedureName is the name of a configuration export procedure.\nCan be used to verify that the passed string does not contain an arbitrary algorithm\nin the 1C\:Enterprise built-in language before using it in Execute and Eval operators\nwhen they are used to dynamically call configuration code methods.\nIf the passed string is not the name of a configuration procedure, an exception is raised.\nIntended to be called from, see procedure ExecuteConfigurationMethod.
